  "body": "<p>Hello everyone, my name is Violeta Scrap and today I want to share with you a layout I created using Amy´s collections.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595493484796-ULM0XMLIYL69RFQYIOYS/9a-Little%2BMoments%2BLayout%2B1.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This layout is about my travel to Malaysia. The layout I’m gonna share with you today is really sweet and whimsical. I used a mix of the two most recent collections Amy designed “Oh happy day” and “Oh a whim”.</p><p>Usually I print my photos with my Canon SELPHY, but I occasionally print at home, I use my INSTAX Share-SP2 It's great for printing from my iPhone, or from my computer.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595493505589-X9EWTC9EWXCNQ72QGH6B/9b-Little%2BMoments%2BLayout%2B2.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I really love how fresh and whimsical this layout looks and the process of making it was nothing but enjoyable.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595493525531-I5XZBUH2D4OCBYN6IZA7/9c-Little%2BMoments%2BLayout%2B3.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This time I wanted to create a white and pink layout, which make the perfect combination for me.</p><p>One of the things I love about using Amy’s collections is that they all have a similar vibe, so even though the color stories and icons may be different, they mix and match so beautifully with one another. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595493542303-48FZR03N9A96VK229I00/9d-.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>My title “Little Moments” was also made using Thickers from “Oh happy life” collection.</p><p>I really love mixing different materials so I included clear stickers, chipboard, stickers, enamels, Thickers and rubber shapes. I also fussy cut some donuts from one of the cut apart sheets and used them around the page as ephemera.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595493560534-QXIZO15QJBDMS8NBAJTK/9e-Little%2BMoments%2BLayout%2B5.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This design is really so easy and fun to make and as I said earlier you only need very minimal supplies.</p><p>I really hope you enjoyed it and you will give it a go.</p><p>Violeta Scrap</p><p><a href=\"http://violetascrap.com/\">Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/violeta_scrap/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/violeta_scrap\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VioletaScrap/\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/VioletaScrap\">YouTube</a></p><p>Supplies: Oh happy life - 12x12 Double Sided Paper - Big deal (376206), Oh happy life - 12x12 Double Sided Paper – Midnight (376200), Oh happy life Collection - Thickers - Wild (376223), On a whim Collection - Clear Stickers, Oh happy life - Clear Stickers, On a whim Collection - Die-cut shapes (378750), On a whim Collection - Sticker Book (378748), Oh happy life Collection - Rubber Shapes (376225), American Crafts - Thickers</p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing this adorable pink layout, Violeta! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop ON A WHIM now! Check your local retailer and online at </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/onawhim\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/amytangerineonawhim\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a></p><p><em>Disclosure: Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
